com.twofortyfouram.locale.sdk.host.ui.loader

Class PluginRegistryLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Loader<D>
      • android.content.AsyncTaskLoader<Map<String,Plugin>>
        • com.twofortyfouram.locale.sdk.host.ui.loader.PluginRegistryLoader

  • @NotThreadSafe
public final class PluginRegistryLoader
extends AsyncTaskLoader<Map<String,Plugin>>
    An AsyncTaskLoader for loading the PluginRegistry.

    In addition to reloading when the registry changes, this also reloads when an interesting configuration change occurs that could affect the display of plug-ins in the UI.
